title: Schobel nets five RBIs as No. 8 Tech tops Radford, 13-8 - VT hokiesports.com
content: Schobel nets five RBIs as No. 8 Tech tops Radford, 13-8  VT hokiesports.com
description: Batting around during its eight-run fifth inning on Wednesday night, the No. 8 Virginia Tech baseball team collected its 25th victory of the season by holding off challenger Radford, 13-8, at Sherman Carter Memorial Stadium.
